# Selection sort.
*ssort(v)
    n is v.length
    i is 0
    while i < n
        m is i
        j is i + 1
        while j < n
            if v.get(j) < v.get(m)
                m is j
            j is j + 1
        if m not equals i
            t is v.get(i)
            v.set(i, v.get(m))
            v.set(m, t)
        i is i + 1

*main
    a is vec(5, 1, 4, 2, 8, 3)
    ssort(a)
    for x in a
        log x
